  ¡§An2-ni kiat-ko2 oe7 chaiN2-iuN7?¡¨ I soe3-siaN mng7, ¡§Li2 siuN7 chaiN2-iuN7?¡¨ Chu2-pit in3. 
  ¡§Chi2-u7 na2 soe-bi5 na7-tiaN7.¡¨ Khek-lah-khek siuN7 ai3 kap i pian7-lun7, chiu7 chip8-tiong i san3-loan7 e5 sim kong2 ¡§Li2 sou2 siuN7 e5 hong-hoat put-ko3 si7 chit8-e5 li2-siong2, si7 boe7 thang sit8-heng5 e5 su7. Kin-a2-jit8 li2 na7 bo5 khan-chai3 chit-e5 siau-sit, chi3-chio2 u7 4,5 pah e5 thok8-chia2 oe7 sit-loh8. It-liu5 e5 jin5-su7, kin-a2-jit8 long2 teh tan2 chit-e5 ki3-su7, li2 m7-thang khoaN3-khin kong-chiong3 e5 ki5-thai7, che si7 toa7 chho3-gou7.¡¨ 
  Chu2-pit cheng7-cheng7 kui2-hun cheng, eng7 koat-i3 e5 gu2-khi3 kong2. ¡§Khek-lah-khek, li2 e5 i3-kian3 boe7 thang cho3 lan2 cho3 su7 e5 phiau-chun2, lan2 e5 i5-it cheng3-tong e5 phiau-chun2 kiam2 m7-si7 kiaN5 Ki-tok sou2 beh kiaN5 e5 mah? Choe3-ko e5 hoat-chek chiu7-si7 hoan7-su7 chu7-mng7 ¡§Na7-si7 Chu2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3?¡¨ Bo5-lun7 kiat-ko2 ju5-ho5, tioh8 chiau3 Chu2 e5 sim-i3 lai5 cho3, oaN7 oe7 lai5 kong2 lang5 ti7 jit8-siong5 e5 seng-oah8 tioh8 eng7 Chu2 choe3 bou5-hoan7 lai5 cho3, kiam2 m7-si7 an2-ni?!¡¨ 
