  No2-ni2-bun5 chu2-pit bo5 koh in3, chi2-u7 teh cheng7-su. ¡§Chit-e5 bun7-te5 i2-au7 chiah koh kong2, kiat-kiok8 li2 tioh8 chiau3 goa2 e5 kau-tai3, m7-thang khan-chai3 hit-e5 poah8-kiau2 e5 siau-sit. Goa2 i2-keng koat-i3 ti7 beh lai5 1 ni5 ku2, beh eng7 ¡§Na7-si7 Chu2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 choe3?¡¨ cho3 phiau-gu2, lai5 pan7 it-chhe3 e5 su7. Goa2 m7-na7 sin3 oe7 seng5-kong, ia7 khak-sin3 beh pi2 koe3-khi3 koh khah toa7 e5 seng5-kong. 
